  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "Dx=(-Ddownq1+Ddownqf1)/(Sqrt[2]);\r\nDy=(-Ddownq1-Ddownqf1)/(I*Sqrt[2]);\r\nDz=Ddownq0;\r\nDdx=ConjugateTranspose[Dx];\r\nDdy=ConjugateTranspose[Dy];\r\nDdz=ConjugateTranspose[Dz];\r\nDxyz={Dx,Dy,Dz};\r\nDdxyz={Ddx,Ddy,Ddz};\r\nDxdt=(-Ddaggerq1+Ddaggerqf1)/(Sqrt[2]);\r\nDydt=(-Ddaggerq1-Ddaggerqf1)/(I*Sqrt[2]);\r\nDzdt=Ddaggerq0;\r\nSimplify[Ddx-Dxdt]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
