  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "Smgdt2[rho_] := Module[{rhoee, smgd6, smgd8},\r\n   rhoee = rho[[1 ;; 2, 1 ;; 2]];   (* 提取激发态 2×2 子块 *)\r\n   \r\n   smgd6 = 2/3*Gms1*(DeltaMat12q1 . rhoee . DeltaMat12dq1 + \r\n                     DeltaMat12q0 . rhoee . DeltaMat12dq0 + \r\n                     DeltaMat12qf1 . rhoee . DeltaMat12dqf1) +\r\n           2/3*Gms2*(DeltaMat32q1 . rhoee . DeltaMat32dq1 + \r\n                     DeltaMat32q0 . rhoee . DeltaMat32dq0 + \r\n                     DeltaMat32qf1 . rhoee . DeltaMat32dqf1);\r\n   \r\n   smgd8 = ConstantArray[0, {8, 8}];\r\n   smgd8[[3 ;; 8, 3 ;; 8]] = smgd6;   (* 塞入右下 6×6 *)\r\n   smgd8\r\n]\r\n",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [],
   "metadata": {},
   "executionSummary": {
    "timing": {
     "startTime": 1781599347196,
     "endTime": 1781599347279
    },
    "executionOrder": 48,
    "success": true
   }
  },
